stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: And so our search for the lost town continues.

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: I don't think we should go that way!

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: There's nothing down here to be afraid of.

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: Nothing except that giant lobster?

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: It's just an underwater parking attendant!

stage_script_messages.name: Lobster
stage_script_messages.message: Move along now - no fleating here!

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: Can you tell us the way to the secret city?

stage_script_messages.name: Lobster
stage_script_messages.message: It would hardly be a secret if I told you!

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: What about treasure? Have you seen any?

stage_script_messages.name: Lobster
stage_script_messages.message: Sure, there's some over there. Now move along!

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: Thanks for the treasure!

stage_script_messages.name: Mystic Fish
stage_script_messages.message: BLUB! BLUB!

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: The Mystic Fish! I wonder if it can help us?

stage_script_messages.name: Mystic Fish
stage_script_messages.message: Who disturbs me?

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: We are looking for adventure, oh wise fish!

stage_script_messages.name: Mystic Fish
stage_script_messages.message: To find a hidden land in the sea...

stage_script_messages.name: Mystic Fish
stage_script_messages.message: Swim down-stream. Now leave me be!

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: I'm not getting out of the submarine. I cant swim!

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: Oh great, a diver who can't swim. That's just brilliant!

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: Is it too late for a swimming lesson?

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: I wish I'd brought my water wings!

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: Be brave and take my flipper.

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: It's okay, there's a lifeguard over there!

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: I can do it! I'm swimming!

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: Look! The hidden city! We did it!

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: Wow! I've never seen so many merpenguins!

stage_script_messages.name: Bubbles
stage_script_messages.message: Welcome travelers!

stage_script_messages.name: Flippers
stage_script_messages.message: New friends! Let me tell you a joke.

stage_script_messages.name: Bubbles
stage_script_messages.message: Oh no, now you've got him started.

stage_script_messages.name: Flippers
stage_script_messages.message: What lies under the ocean and shivers?

stage_script_messages.name: Flippers
stage_script_messages.message: A nervous wreck!

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: LOL! That's terrible!

stage_script_messages.name: Bubbles
stage_script_messages.message: Enough, Flippers! Let them explore the city.

stage_script_messages.name: Flippers
stage_script_messages.message: Welcome to Penglantis - our home is yours!

stage_script_messages.name: Daisy
stage_script_messages.message: This is such an adventure!

stage_script_messages.name: Fiesel
stage_script_messages.message: And its only just begun!

stage_script_messages.name: Director:
stage_script_messages.message: Places please!

stage_script_messages.name: Director:
stage_script_messages.message: Start swimming!

stage_script_messages.name: Director:
stage_script_messages.message: Excellent work, team. Keep it up!

stage_script_messages.name: Director:
stage_script_messages.message: Fantastic acting. Well done!

stage_script_messages.name: Director:
stage_script_messages.message: Curtain call!

evergreen.town: Welcome to the Town Center!|This spot is the heart of the island.|From here, you can get coffee|...dance at the Night Club...|...or check out the Gift Shop for some accessories.
evergreen.coffee: This is the Coffee Shop.|The coffee here is delicious!|You can also click the bag of coffee beans...|...if you want to play Bean Counters.|Or, serve up smoothies in Smoothie Smash!
evergreen.book: Here is the Book Room.|Click on the bookshelf to read something.|You can also play a game called Mancala.|It's a fun game, but difficult to learn.|Read How to Play Mancala before playing...|then play a few games to learn how it works.
evergreen.dance: Welcome to the Night Club.|This is THE place for dance parties.|That green puffle on the speaker is called the Keeper...|He was gone for a short while recently...|So it's good to have him back!
evergreen.lounge: This is the second floor of the Night Club.|It is called the Lounge.|The Lounge is great for relaxing after dancing.|There are also fun arcade games here!
evergreen.eco: This is the Recycling Plant!|Throw your recycling into the Recycletron 3000...|...and turn rubbish into useful things!
evergreen.shop: This is the Gift Shop.|You can buy clothes from the monthly catalog.|Colors and backgrounds can be bought as well.|Use coins you have earned from playing games.
evergreen.village: Here we have the Ski Village.|There's the Ski Hill, Ski Lodge and the Sports Shop...|...where you can buy lots of different sports equipment!
evergreen.sportshop: Welcome to the Sports Shop.|Here, you can buy all sorts of sports equipment.|There's absolutely nothing behind the rightmost change room.
evergreen.lodge: The Ski Lodge is a great place to warm up.|Or, you can play Find Four with friends.|You can also visit the Ice Pond out the back door.
evergreen.attic: This is the Lodge Attic.|It has been used to store just about anything!|It also has more Find Four tables.
evergreen.mtn: If you like to sled, come to Ski Hill!|I guess it should be called Sled Hill.|Bunny Hill is for newcomers, Ridge Run is only for pros.|The drop is almost straight down!
evergreen.pet: The Pet Shop is where you can adopt a puffle.|Puffles are animals native to Club Penguin.|They have different colors and personalities.|They all like penguins, and make great pets.
evergreen.dojo: Here we are in the Dojo.|Learn to become a Ninja with Card-Jitsu.|Train and earn belts to progress.|Only the dedicated will succeed.
evergreen.courtyard: This is the Courtyard.|It was covered in snow for many moons!|Enter the Dojo and take the path of the Ninja.
evergreen.hideout: Welcome to the Ninja Hideout!|Only ninjas have access to this special room.|Here you will find the Martial Artworks catalog...|Where you can buy lots of ninja clothing and furniture.
evergreen.pizza: This is the Pizza Parlor.|Come here to order the best pizza.|If you go into the kitchen...|...you can help make pizzas with the Pizzatron.|Also, serve pizzas by visiting the pizza oven!
evergreen.plaza: Greetings from the Plaza!|From here, you can visit the Pizza Parlor...|...watch a play at the Stage...|...or you can adopt a puffle at the Pet Shop.
evergreen.beach: This is the Beach, home of the Lighthouse.|It is a great place to relax in the sun.|Sometimes you see the pirate ship docked here!
evergreen.lighthouse: This is the Lighthouse...|...the tallest building in Club Penguin.|Take a look at the pictures on the wall...|...or grab a new instrument and perform on stage.|Go upstairs to find the Beacon!
evergreen.beacon: The Beacon holds the Lighthouse spotlight...|...and a telescope that you can look through.|And if you thought penguins could not fly...|...you should try the Jetpack game on the right.
evergreen.ship: This is the pirate ship, the Migrator. Arrrr!|Rockhopper sails the seas in this ship.
evergreen.shiphold: This is the ship's cargo hold.|Due to the crash the Migrator has faced...|...Rockhopper couldn't put his loot here.|Hopefully he will next time!
evergreen.shipnest: This is called the Crow's Nest...|...where Yarr keeps a lookout.|You can get a great view...|...of the island!
evergreen.shipquarters: This is the Captain's Quarters!|Rockhopper spends a lot of time here.|Look at the corkboard for his photos!|Or, grab a friend and hunt for some treasure!
evergreen.dock: Welcome to the Dock.|You can play Hydro-Hopper here.|Take a ride on a tube behind the speedboat.
evergreen.forts: These Snow Forts are fun for snowball fights.|Click the snowball icon to throw one.|Over there is the Club Penguin Journey clock.|It shows the time in the Penguin Standard Time Zone.
evergreen.rink: Welcome to the Stadium, sports fans!|Take part in the action and start a game!|Or grab a snack and watch from the bleachers.
evergreen.boiler: This is the Boiler Room.|It gives electricity and heat to the island.|Here you can read old editions of the newspaper.|It is a great way to learn about Club Penguin Journey.
evergreen.berg: This is the Iceberg. It is a secret room.|In the distance you can see Club Penguin.|If you want to dive into the ocean depths...|...try out the Aqua Grabber!
evergreen.cave: Here we have the Cave, which has its own pool.|It also has windows to see underwater.|Wait a moment, and a crab may walk by.
evergreen.shack: Welcome to the Mine Shack...|Home of the Mine and the Community Garden!|Help water the garden by throwing snowballs...|...into the green bucket.|Beside the beautiful tree is the Recycling Plant...|...where we use garbage to make useful stuff!
evergreen.mine: This is the Mine.|Puffles like exploring tunnels...|... and sometimes get trapped inside.|They need your help to rescue them!
evergreen.forest: Welcome to the Forest!|Go to the Cove by walking down those stairs...|...or take the top right path to the Mine Shack...|...and help out at the garden.
evergreen.cove: This is the Cove!|It is a wonderful, secluded spot.|You can go swimming in the shallow water here.|Or, test your surf skill and catch some waves!
evergreen.boxdimension: Welcome to the Box Dimension.|This mysterious place is the source of all boxes.|Please leave the laws of physics at the door.
evergreen.cavemine: Here we have the Mine Cave...|Many penguins mine the gold reserves down here.|So grab a hardhat and start digging!
evergreen.hiddenlake: Wow! This place is the Hidden Lake...|Where did all this treasure come from, I wonder?|And it looks like there's a door under the water...
evergreen.underwater: BLUB! This place is Underwater...|Look at all the colorful fish and plants! And treasure!|This sure is unusual...
evergreen.stage: Welcome to the Stage. Tickets please!|Many different plays are performed here.|A new play is put on every month or so!|If you're interested in a job...|...actors, directors, and stage hands are needed!
evergreen.welcome: This is the Welcome Room!|This is often the first place you visit.|If Club Penguin Journey is having a party...|...this room is usually well decorated for it.
evergreen.tourhq: This is the Tour Headquarters.|You can become a tour guide here...|...or go upstairs to view the island from the Lookout!|Click the box over there to send a suggestion for the game.
evergreen.lookout: Here we are in the Lookout.|This room has the best view of the island!|Be sure to check the room during events!
evergreen.oldboiler: The Old Boiler is quite unusual.|Penguins seem to have found this room by accident.|Be sure not to walk into this room's boiler.
evergreen.icepond: This is the Ice Pond!|Here, you can go ice fishing...|...or watch Fluffy the Fish grow big!
evergreen.hq: This room... is top secret, I can not tell you what goes on in here.|Oh, wait we are all agents here.| This room is the Agents Headquarters.|You can get here through the Sports Shop.|Or, you can just use your spy phone.|Click on a TV to go somewhere.

party.party1: Check out the Music Maker 3000!|Let's try lighting up the stage...|with some new moves!
party.party2: This is the Night Club Rooftop!|Check out those awesome lights!|Bust a move on the dance floor...|or try out the Music Player 3000!
party.party3: Welcome backstage!|This area is strictly for VIPs.|You never know who you'll find here chilling after a gig!
party.party4: Love to jam and dance with your buddies?|The Casa Fiesta's a GIANT party.|There's only one rule...|Have fun!

scripts: Sailin' the seas be the life for me
I be causin' a roarin' ruckus with ye!
ARRR! how be ye this fine day?
The fastest ship on the seas!
It be faster than a slippery squid
It be faster than a greased cannonball
It be faster than Rookie chasing a sandwich
And let me tell ye mateys, he be pretty fast!
This be the barrel where I keep me stinky cheese
And this also be a barrel of stinky cheese
And this barrel... stinky cheese too
Perhaps I have too much stinky cheese
That be a joke, HAR HAR HAR!
You can never have too much stinky cheese
No, there's no crow up here
It just be a strange name
Ahhh, that one gets me every time
There be a memory dear to me heart
It be the time I meet me best friend...
I was sailin' me ship for new lands
All kinds of adventures I be havin'
Avast! In the sea there be a strange sight
It be a piece of driftwood with a puffle atop it
And sped to save that puffle's life
Ay, he warmed to me like a clam to a shell
and now he be me first mate!
It be the Coins for Change parties
Ye be a fine and generous crew
and ye donate ya hard earned coins
T'is a fine thing ye be doing
Arrrr... ye think this be a tear in me eye?
Nay, just a bit of sea salt, mateys!
It be the time ye helped rebuild the Migrator
A lily-livered ice berg crashed into me ship!
The migrator sunk to the bottom of the bay, it did!
But ye really came through for me, mateys
Ye worked hard to salvage her from the depths
and finally the Migrator was rebuilt!
Of course those pesky crabs sunk it later
But ye helped me with those scallywags too!
Mateys! how about a pirate parade?
Up the ladder to the Crow's Nest!
Last one to the Beach be a wet fish!
and a bottle o cream soda!
AVAST this be the place for pirates!
Who be servin' the food in this place?
HAR HAR HAR I be jokin'
Play a sea shanty me matey!
ARR ye be a fine piano player!
Here be my favoritest sea song
WE BE A CREW OF PIRATES
WE DRINK BARRELS OF CREAM SODA
AND EAT TONS OF STINKY CHEESE
BUT THE THING THAT WE LIKE BEST
I be in the mood for squid pizza
What else ye want on it, mateys?
Do ye like these toppings, mateys?
Arr...these pizzas not be sittin' well
That be the best pizza I ever had!
I got a case o' the pizza toots
Now that's what I be callin' FAIR winds
It be these fish yar har har!
Arr she be a fine ship!
Me ship be full o' treasure for everyone!
It be the pirate's life for me
I be the CAPTAIN of me ship!
Find me key to open me quarters!
Me journal be in the Newsroom
Ye hard work on me ship be noted! Thank ye!
Aye me key be hidden on this island!
Have ye found the key to me quarters?
What ye all think of me Captain's Quarters?
I see ye be liking me Treasure Hunt
Watch where ye be aimin those snowballs!
We be settlin this score the old fashioned way...
YE BE RUEIN THE DAY YE MESSED WITH ME
This be the greatest snowball fight ever fought
ARR, I be playin hide and seek!
Hide n' Seek be a good game for pirates
It be makin' ye could at findin things
This be a good place for a story
Who be tellin this tale? Ye or me?
I swear on me beard this be true!
Can ye guess what happened next?
Ye won't believe what happened next
That be the end o' me tale!
Yarr harr! Ye be a fine bunch o' listeners!!
when a strange creature came upon me
and he smelled of the sea
his teeth were as BIG as a whale
AND HE BE LOOKIN' MIGHTY HUNGRY
I feared he was to eat me
can you guess what happened next?
It be a tangled mess o' seaweed
And in it YARR be hidin'
So me treasure be safe after all!
burying me treasure on a strange new island
a group of treasure huntin' flamingos came me way
I not be sharin' with the likes of them
ye never know when they be tellin' the truth
they promised loads of cream soda
just as I be drinkin' me cream soda
they made off with me treasure
left me with nothin' but me friend YARR
Good thing I had some coins hiddin' in me beard!
Tryin' to follow me treasure map
When I be seein' a tiny pirate parade
They be marchin' across the sand
And even be havin' stinky cheese
It be ants with little eye patches!
When I followed 'em to their anthill
I saw where they be gettin' the cheese!
It be comin' from me own Migrator!
So I parlayed with their queen
And they helped be find treasure!
But I had to leave them me cheese
And I be sailin' the seas
When I saw black sails off me port bow
It be lookin' like a pirate battle!
But I be hollerin' to the cap'n
We both be pirates lookin' fer loot!
So the cap'n and I find an accord
That be meanin' we make a deal
So we both be gettin' new treasure!
ARR! I be proud to be ye friend!
Make sure to claim me background
It be a fine picture of me! YAR HAR!
Me beard keeps me warm on me travels!
It be good for storing things too
and an extra pair o boots!
Yarr be keeping lookout at me ship
Yarr be right here beside me!
Me favorite animal be a puffle!
Pirates! What be ye favorite animal?
I likes pirate music that I can dance a jig to!
What be ye favorite sport mateys?!
Me favorite sport be a snowball fight
Arr what be ye favorite hobby?
Me hobbies be sailin' and treasure huntin'
Find me key to open me quarters!
Me journal be in the Newsroom
Farewell me hearties! I be leavin' now!
Me hearties! thanks for the fun!
This be time for me to go!
